node.text: Whether she went for plunging necklines, sky-high slits or sexy cutouts, Zendaya has continued to out-do herself on the red carpet this year. 😍 "We have such a relationship that there's no fear when it comes to fashion," says Zendaya's longtime image architect Law Roach in PEOPLE's 2021 Style Issue, on newsstands Friday. "There's nothing she won't try. She's fearless." 👏 Tap the bio link for more on her "unexpected" and "constantly evolving" style. | 📷: Bertrand Rindoff Petroff/Getty Images, David Fisher/Shutterstock, Chris Pizzello/Pool/Shutterstock
